Introducing the New Roadmap for Sugar Kingdom Odyssey 

Dear Sugar Kingdom Odyssey Community,

We are excited to unveil the next phase of our journey, as we build upon the foundations of our innovative gaming ecosystem. The months ahead bring significant developments designed to enhance player engagement such as the tournament mode.

Below, we detail two major milestones that will shape the future of Sugar Kingdom Odyssey, we decided to bring this features in the following months:

1. Launch of NFT Minting in December 2024 
In December, we will introduce a new feature that integrates Non-Fungible Tokens (NFTs) into the Sugar Kingdom Odyssey ecosystem. These NFTs are designed to play a pivotal role in enhancing gameplay and expanding the utility of SKO tokens.

How the Minting Process Works
Players will have the opportunity to mint NFTs by burning 1,000 SKO tokens per NFT.
This initiative will contribute to a more strategic use of SKO while simultaneously introducing unique digital assets into the game. You will be able to check all of this information and the terms & conditions of participation in our whitepaper: https://docs.sugarkingdom.io

Applications of NFTs
Game Enhancements: NFTs will serve as boosts within the game, offering players enhanced abilities that improve their chances of excelling in competitive modes. They will also provide access to exclusive gaming features, creating a more personalized and dynamic experience.

Customization: Use NFTs as skins to showcase your unique style and identity in the game.

Access Requirements: Specific features, such as the upcoming Tower Defense Game, will require players to hold at least 1 NFT to participate. This integration of NFTs not only enriches the gameplay experience but also fosters strategic thinking as players decide how to best utilize their resources.

2. Tower Defense Game Launching in March 2025 
The next major step in our roadmap is the launch of the highly anticipated Tower Defense Game, scheduled for March 2025. This addition is designed to diversify the Sugar Kingdom Odyssey experience by introducing a new layer of strategy and competition.

What Makes the Tower Defense Game Unique?
Exclusive Gameplay: This game mode introduces a strategic format where players must defend their resources against challenging waves of opponents.
Access will be limited to players holding at least 1 NFT, ensuring a high-quality experience for participants.

NFT Integration: Players can leverage their NFTs not only as entry passes but also as tools to gain gameplay advantages, such as faster resource generation or improved defense capabilities.

Seamless Ecosystem Expansion: The Tower Defense Game builds upon our existing foundation, complementing the Match-3 Tournament Mode that was successfully launched earlier this year.
Our goal with the Tower Defense Game is to offer players a deeper, more tactical gaming experience while reinforcing the value of NFTs within the Sugar Kingdom Odyssey universe.

Roadmap highlights
Enhanced Utility for SKO Tokens is a must. By introducing NFT minting as a burning mechanism, we are fostering a more sustainable ecosystem and providing players with meaningful ways to engage with the currency. Also, the addition of the Tower Defense Game represents our interest in expanding the types of games available within Sugar Kingdom Odyssey, ensuring variety with NFTs serving multiple functions.

When can we expect the NFT launch?
We will be dropping updates about it in our discord, now interact with this tweet and get VIP role ( that give you access to the VIP discord channel and will enable you to be whitelisted for the mint!).

We keep open to your suggestions, do not hesitate in letting us know your preferences in discord tickets!

Best,
The Sugar Kingdom Odyssey Team.

直播现状
今年，http://Pump.fun在加密圈大火，这不仅仅是一个发币平台，更是为那些没有任何技术背景的普通投资者开启了Meme世界的大门。仅仅用了217天就创造了上亿美元的营收，每一个怀揣梦想的普通人都能在这里发币。

人人都能发币好似人人都能做自媒体，要想抢占流量就必须抓住有限用户群体的注意力，而meme又与金钱强挂钩，别有用心的人就会更加不择手段。

有一位开发者叫Mikol，他曾在http://Pump.fun上推出一个名为TruthOrDare（DARE）的meme，当时http://Pump.fun还没有直播功能，Mikol在twich上直播往身上浇异丙醇，让朋友向他的方向发射烟花。他的身体被点燃，全身三度烧伤送往医院，代币DARE在Mikol烧伤那日获得12倍涨幅，次日又迅速归零。

加密乱象
http://Pump.fun的崛起使加密市场迎来了全民发币热潮，每天有成千上万的新代币在Solana链上发行，http://Pump.fun收入屡破新高，横扫24个协议总和，与此同时不少竞品平台纷纷涌现，大家都意识到了当赌徒没有开赌场赚钱。
